org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.ietf.params.xml.ns.yang.ietf.netconf.monitoring.rev101004.netconf.state.datastores

Interface Datastore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Datastore>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Datastores>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<DatastoreKey>

    public interface Datastore
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.ChildOf<Datastores>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Augmentable<Datastore>, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.Identifiable<DatastoreKey>
    List of NETCONF configuration datastores supported by the NETCONF server and related information.

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module ietf-netconf-monitoring
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/ietf-netconf-monitoring.yang): 

     list datastore {
     key "name"
     leaf name {
         type netconf-datastore-type;
     }
     container locks {
         choice lock-type {
             case global-lock {
                 container global-lock {
                     leaf locked-by-session {
                         type uint32;
                     }
                     leaf locked-time {
                         type date-and-time;
                     }
                     uses netconf-state;
                 }
             }
             case partial-lock {
                 list partial-lock {
                     key "lock-id"
                     leaf lock-id {
                         type uint32;
                     }
                     leaf locked-by-session {
                         type uint32;
                     }
                     leaf locked-time {
                         type date-and-time;
                     }
                     leaf-list select {
                         type xpath1.0;
                     }
                     leaf-list locked-node {
                         type instance-identifier;
                     }
                     uses netconf-state;
                 }
             }
         }
         grouping lock-info {
             leaf locked-by-session {
                 type uint32;
             }
             leaf locked-time {
                 type date-and-time;
             }
         }
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is ietf-netconf-monitoring/netconf-state/datastores/datastore

    To create instances of this class use DatastoreBuilder.

      • getLocks

        Locks getLocks()
        The NETCONF and operations allow a client to lock specific resources in a datastore. The NETCONF server will prevent changes to the locked resources by all sessions except the one that acquired the lock(s). Monitoring information is provided for each datastore entry including details such as the session that acquired the lock, the type of lock (global or partial) and the list of locked resources. Multiple locks per datastore are supported.
